descriptor.name: Wet N Wild Lipstick for Womens
descriptor.short_desc: Wet N Wild Lipstick for Womens
descriptor.long_desc: Take on the world with your power and sass! SUGAR presents the invincible and super awe-inspiring Wonder Woman collection – three impressive ranges of bravely-pigmented lipsticks in charismatic finishes with ten lipsticks in each range and two fearless makeup palettes that play up your strength and beauty like no other. Inspired by the iconic heroine Wonder Woman, this grit-ful and vibrant hued limited edition makeup collection reflects everything she stands for – a boon companion, a true friend and the most trusted soul. Coming right from the league of superheroes, this fantasy makeup collection cased in royal red, bold blue and regal gold packaging adorned with Wonder Woman’s iconic ‘W’ Logo is the ultimate beacon of oomph and will empower you to create fierce beauty looks that let you rule the universe. It's time to play up your strengths and embrace your inner superheroine. Kaboom!!!

@ondc/org/statutory_reqs_packaged_commod.common_or_generic_name_of_commodity: Wet N Wild Lipstick for Womens
